=== 評價 ===
《出埃及記：天地王者》獲得的評價多為負面，雖然演員們的演技和視覺效果獲得一致好評，但同時也批評劇本的單薄、缺乏角色的發展性與整體的單薄<ref>{{cite web | url = http://screenrant.com/exodus-gods-kings-reviews-preview/ | title = ‘Exodus: Gods and Kings’ Early Reviews: Ridley Scott’s Epic Draws Mixed Reaction | author = Sandy Schaefer | publisher = ''Screenrant'' | date = 2014-12-02 | accessdate = 2014-12-04 | archive-date = 2014-12-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141203194622/http://screenrant.com/exodus-gods-kings-reviews-preview/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。於[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]根據128條影評持有27％的新鮮度，平均分數4.8／10，在觀眾評分方面，則根據59543位[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]的用戶發表的評論持有著35%的評價，平均評分2.8/5 。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/exodus_gods_and_kings/ | title=Exodus: Gods and Kings | work=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] | publisher=[[Flixster|Flixster]] | accessdate=2014-12-09 | archive-date=2014-12-27 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141227042837/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/exodus_gods_and_kings | dead-url=no }}</ref>。在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]基於41位評論得分52（滿分100），評價好壞參雜<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/exodus-gods-and-kings | title=Exodus: Gods and Kings Reviews | work=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] | publisher=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]] | accessdate=2014-12-09 | archive-date=2014-12-10 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141210203408/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/exodus-gods-and-kings | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

